# Settings Page — Feature Blueprint (Clean + Professional)

• UI Mode
  - [ ] Minimal Clean LIGHT
  - [ ] Minimal Clean DARK
  - Radio-style behavior (only one active at a time)

• API Key Status
  - Shows each provider’s key as:
    - Encrypted / Decrypted
    - Valid / Invalid
  - Quick indicators for OpenAI, Anthropic, Gemini, Local

• Storage Location
  - Display current storage path
  - Option to change local storage directory
  - Option to link cloud storage (Google Drive, OneDrive, Dropbox, etc.)

• UI Adjustments
  - Manual / Automatic sizing to fit environment
  - Text size selector
  - Font selector (clean professional fonts only)

• General Behavior
  - All critical screens (Security, Settings, API Keys) use minimal clean UI
  - Chat + Projects use neon theme
  - Settings acts as the control center for all app-wide preferences
